Veteran broadcaster, Claire Mawisa has turned the big four zero. The former child-star, turned television royalty held a joined 40th birthday dinner with two of her close friends and called it #TheUltimate40th. All three of them dressed up in stunning, matching red dresses and were surrounded by close family and friends. A few familiar faces also made an appearance at the dinner. The iconic, Thebe even gave a special performance. After the dinner, Claire took to Twitter to share 40 of her biggest life lessons. Spotted on the evening were Thula Sindi and Luphi Ngcayisa.  